    "The primary studies included in the survey were comparatively examined in terms of their main findings and practical implications.",
    "A total of 16 primary studies were reviewed.Therefore, they do not engage in the synthesis of evidence that formulates RQs and identifies and synthesizes data related to these RQs.",
